### Submit Lawyer Verification
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lawyer-verification/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deepesh",
  "email": "deepesh@gmail.com",
  "barCouncilId": "BC123",
  "city": "Gurgaon",
  "state": "Haryana",
  "specialization": "Criminal Law",
  "experience": "2 years",
  "documentUrl": "resume.pdf",
  "userId": "user123",
  "status": "PENDING"
}

### Get All Verifications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lawyer-verification/all

### Get Pending Verifications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lawyer-verification/pending